title: Does America Go To War For Profit?! Here's The Answer
description:
I spoke with Richard Hanania on my podcast. He is a writer, researcher and President of the Center for the Study of Partisanship and Ideology and a Research Fellow at Defense Priorities. We discussed who benefits the most from American Foreign Policy. #War #IndustrialMilitaryComplex #NATO

description:
